            OR choose Hangman’s Trail (50 yds.) that has a shallow dig to recover a small leather pouch with unknown contents. The team debates then runs on their trail of choice, not knowing if the dig site will yield the golden nugget. At dig sites, there are mining picks to use in reaching the “pay dirt” 
